# Cogito — AI Cognitive Companion · Prototype Walkthrough

**Files built:** [index.html](file:///Users/angela/Downloads/Antigravity/index.html), [style.css](file:///Users/angela/Downloads/Antigravity/style.css), [app.js](file:///Users/angela/Downloads/Antigravity/app.js)  
**Location:** `/Users/angela/Downloads/Antigravity/`  
**Open with:** Double-click `index.html` in Finder (no server needed)

---

## What Was Built

A fully interactive, no-backend frontend prototype for the **Cogito** AI cognitive companion.

### 3-Panel Layout

| Panel | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| **Left — Problem** | Drag-and-drop / paste / click-to-browse screenshot upload, topic tags, difficulty indicator, live session stats |
| **Centre — Think Aloud** | Conversation area with user & AI bubbles, streaming AI text, KaTeX math rendering, hint/fallacy/theory callout cards |
| **Right — Your Path** | SVG flowchart that builds node-by-node in green (✓ correct), red (✗ error), yellow (△ missed) |

